{
  "stem": "11611.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I say, this was both part of the so-called Aryanization program and also part of German occupation policy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans had the notion that when they had successfully conquered all of Europe and all the world, they wanted to own it as well in the most direct sense.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had an economic policy called Verflechtung, which means interlacing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Interlacing meant taking over and Germans controlling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a rather euphemistic term for grabbing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was-- it's all prohibited by traditional war crimes law, prohibited by the Hague Conventions very directly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Dresdner Bank was known in Germany as the SS bank, which was a very favorable reputation in Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one of their other activities was making loans, interest free or an extremely low interest rate for building concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Building concentration camps required money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They furnished money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That charge did not stick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The first charge stuck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "American, American judges would not find anything wrong in a bank making a low-interest loan.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, business is business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They thought this was too close to traditional banking business, the financing of concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In other words, if an American bank did it, it was OK too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The vice president of the Reichsbank was charged with something different.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Emil Puhl, P-U-H-L.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was one of Schacht's deputies, Schacht having been acquitted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Puhl, I think, was in charge of running the vaults of the Reichsbank, which were filled with gold teeth, gold wedding rings, gold fountain pens, gold wrist watches, any form of gold that could be taken off the form of-- off the bodies of corpses in extermination camps-- Auschwitz, Treblinka, Sobibor, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was his specialty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these things weren't mounds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were mountains of gold.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
